cBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013639, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, all praise be to You for You have guided me. All praise be to You for You have favored me. All praise be to You for You have honored me. All praise be to You for all of the good turns that You have bestowed upon me. O Allah, (please do) accept my prayer and supplication, purify my heart, expand my breast for me, and accept my repentance. You are indeed the Oft-returning to mercy and the All-merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Tere liye hamd hai keh Tu ne mujh ko hidaayat di, Tere liye hamd hai keh Tu ne mujh ko bartari bakhshi, Tere liye hamd hai keh Tu ne mujh ko badaayi ataa ki aur Tere liye hamd hai keh Tu ne mujh ko har achchhi aazmaaish mein daala. Ay Ma’bood! Qabool farma meri namaz aur meri dua, paak kar mere dil ko, khol de mere seene ko aur meri taubah qabool kar, keh yaqeenan Tu bohot taubah qabool karne waala maher-baan hai.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! تیرے لئے حمد ہے کہ تو نے مجھ کو ہدایت دی تیرے لئے حمد ہے کہ تو نے مجھ کو برتری بخشی تیرے لئے حمد ہے کہ تو نے مجھ کو بڑائی عطا کی اور تیرے لئے حمد ہے کہ تو نے مجھ کو ہر اچھی آزمائش میں ڈالا اے معبود! قبول فرما میری نماز اور میری دعا،پاک کرمیرے دل کو، کھول دے میرے سینے کو اور میری توبہ قبول کر کہ یقینًا تو بہت توبہ قبول کرنے والا مہربان ہے۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA LAKAL HAMDO A’LAA MAA HADAYTANEE WA LAKAL HAMDO A’LAA MAA FAZZALTANEE WA LAKAL HAMDO A’LAA MAA SHARRAFTANEE WA LAKAL HAMDO A’LAA KULLE BA-LAAA-IN HASANE-NIB-TALAYTANEE ALLAAHUMMA TAQABBAL SALAATEE WA DO-A’AA-EE WA TAHHIR QALBEE WASH-RAH LEE SADREE WA TUB A’LAYYA INNAKA ANTAT TAWWAABUR RAHEEM.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ لَكَ الْحَمْدُ عَلٰی مَا هَدَیْتَنِیْ وَلَكَ الْحَمْدُ عَلٰی مَا فَضَّلْتَنِیْ وَلَكَ الْحَمْدُ عَلٰی مَا شَرَّفْتَنِیْ وَلَكَ الْحَمْدُ عَلٰی كُلِّ بَلَآءٍ حَسَنٍ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": " نِ", "ArabicText2": "ابْتَلَیْتَنِیْ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ تَقَبَّلْ صَلٰوتِیْ وَدُعَآئِیْ وَطَهِّرْ قَلْبِیْ وَاشْرَحْ لِیْ صَدْرِیْ وَتُبْ عَلَیَّ اِنَّكَ اَنْتَ التَّوَّابُ الرَّحِیْمُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": n